---
/**
 * Hero principal de la home
 */
---

<section class="relative pt-28 pb-20 sm:pt-36 sm:pb-28 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background decoration -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-brand-100/40 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/4"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-brand-50/60 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/4"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Badge -->
      <div class="reveal inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-brand-50 border border-brand-200 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-brand-700 mb-8">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
        +50 Sistemas implementados
      </div>

      <!-- Title -->
      <h1 class="reveal text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
        Sistemas de gestión<br class="hidden sm:block" />
        que <span class="text-brand-500">sí vas a usar</span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <p class="reveal text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
        Si probaste mil cosas para organizarte y al final siempre volvés al Excel porque es lo más cómodo,
        <strong class="text-slate-700">estás en el lugar correcto.</strong>
      </p>

      <!-- Buttons -->
      <div class="reveal flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4" style="transition-delay: 0.3s;">
        <a href="#catalogo" class="btn-primary text-base">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2zM14 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z"></path>
          </svg>
          Ver sistemas armados
        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/5491128839719" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-secondary text-base">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#25D366]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"></path>
